      "content": "Dotfiles Chezmoi Architecture (2026-03-04): Use chezmoi for multi-machine dotfiles with templates, secrets integration (age/1Password), and idempotent scripts. Rules: template all config via .chezmoi.toml.tmpl with promptBoolOnce variables; make run_once_ scripts idempotent; never commit secrets; use .chezmoidata/ cache for secrets. Avoid: inline password manager calls, non-idempotent scripts, runtime conditionals instead of init-time flags. Full: docs/research/dotfiles-chezmoi-architecture.md. Review: 2026-09-04."
